<i>adverb</i>: 척척 [척척], 착착 [착착], 서서히 [서ː서히], 빤히 [빤ː히], 꾸준히 [꾸준히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>척척 [척척]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quickly without hesitation</dd><br>
<dd>전혀 망설이지 않고 선뜻선뜻 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of doing a certain act swiftly and without hesitation.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily</dd><br>
<dd>일이 막힘이 없이 아주 잘되어 가는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of something going smoothly without any problems.</dd><br>
<dd>3. steadily</dd><br>
<dd>질서 있게 조화를 이루어 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In an orderly and systematic fashion.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>착착 [착착]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quickly without hesitation</dd><br>
<dd>망설이지 않고 빠르고 시원하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of doing a certain act swiftly, vigorously, and without hesitation.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily</dd><br>
<dd>일이 막힘없이 잘되어 가는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of something going smoothly without any problems.</dd><br>
<dd>3. steadily</dd><br>
<dd>조화를 이루어 질서 있게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In an orderly and systematic fashion.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>서서히 [서ː서히]</dt><br>
<dd>gradually; steadily</dd><br>
<dd>조금씩 느리게.</dd><br>
<dd>Slowly and little by little.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>빤히 [빤ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. brightly</dd><br>
<dd>어둠 속에서 밝은 빛이 비치어 환하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being slightly bright as a light shines in darkness.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plainly; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일의 결과나 상태가 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the result or state of something is clear.</dd><br>
<dd>3. fixedly; steadily; intently</dd><br>
<dd>바라보는 것이 정면으로 또렷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's staring eyes being clear.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꾸준히 [꾸준히]</dt><br>
<dd>steadily; persistently</dd><br>
<dd>거의 변함이 없이 한결같이.</dd><br>
<dd>Consistently.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>